orld leader in corneal remodeling avedro’s patented crosslinking technology consisting of drug formulations and medical devices are approved for sale in numerous countries around the globe in the united states the company sells an orphan drug indicated for the treatment of progressive keratoconus which was fda approved in  avedro continues to develop proprietary cornea crosslinking products for the treatment of keratoconus a sightthreatening disease and for refractive correction view source version on businesswirecom httpwwwbusinesswirecomnewshome02enavedro contactavedro incdavid iannetta infoavedrocomormedia contactbiocomm network incmichele gray 99michelegraymecomcopyright business wire information contained on this page is provided by an independent thirdparty content provider frankly and this site make no warranties or representations in connection therewith if you are affiliated with this page and have questions or removal reuqests please contact pressreleasesfranklyinccom current conditions  day forecastlatest weathercasthourly forecasttexas radar eyewire today  donald j zurbay joins avedro’s board of directors home eyewiretv news events login username password home eyewiretv news events donald j zurbay joins avedro’s board of directors source avedro tuesday july    managementleadership  avedro avedro announced that donald j zurbay has been elected to its board of directors a veteran finance executive with more than 2 years in financial operations and accounting mr zurbay is the former vice president and chief financial officer cfo of st jude medical a fortune 00 multinational medical device company during his tenure at st jude medical mr zurbay helped guide the company through significant growth and expansion including  acquisitions and ultimately the recent transaction to sell st jude medical to abbott for 2 billion “don is an accomplished business leader with a proven track record of developing strategy and driving execution for business growth he will be a